data.description: Well Maintained spacious ranch style home located in wonderful school district in the heart of Lawrenceville. This charming home offers spacious eat-in kitchen with newer stainless steel refrigerator and range to stay, oversized family room, formal dining area. New windows on the front and rear of home recently installed. beautiful LVP flooring located in family room, kitchen and dining room compliment this cozy floor plan. Private master bedroom with vaulted ceilings and large walk-in closet. Cozy secondary bedrooms located on the other side of home offering privacy for your kiddos or guest. Oversized bonus room perfect for theater room or additional living space. Well manicured corner lot will not last long!
